{"type": "article", "id": 18802, "title": "致敬 Giorgio Morandi 的玻璃灯", "description": "", "date": "2015-12-10T07:30:15Z", "super_tag": "", "tags": [], "category": 25, "column": 28, "author": 161922, "comment_count": 1, "praise_count": 26, "image": "img/article/article_show/20160702115150t9FBJvy4OLgo6dN3.jpg", "contents": "\n\n<p>\r\n\t这些灯是对意大利艺术家 Giorgio Morandi（乔治·莫兰迪）的致敬，白色的灯泡下面连接着像瓶子一样的底座，神似 Giorgio Morandi 所画的带有抒情色彩的静物。三盏灯的底座分别以蓝色、粉色和绿色为主，除了有半透明的彩色玻璃，还有一圈带有细微凹凸纹路的陶瓷制品，可以增加握住时的摩擦，也很有质感。白色的灯光正好照在下面的瓶子上，有光影的细微变化。\r\n</p>\r\n<p style=\"text-align:center;\">\r\n\t<img src=\"img/uploads/201607021151484r0318vmtQ5py2UK.jpg\" width=\"600\" height=\"800\" title=\" \" alt=\" \" data-ratio=\"1.33333333\" data-format=\"jpeg\"> \r\n</p>\r\n<p style=\"text-align:center;\">\r\n\t<img src=\"img/uploads/20160702115149sOnJ4D5mbqEWXU90.jpg\" width=\"600\" height=\"800\" title=\" \" alt=\" \" data-ratio=\"1.33333333\" data-format=\"jpeg\"> \r\n</p>\r\n<p style=\"text-align:center;\">\r\n\t<img src=\"img/uploads/20160702115149p4dxXMRqDncNWUTv.jpg\" width=\"600\" height=\"800\" title=\" \" alt=\" \" data-ratio=\"1.33333333\" data-format=\"jpeg\"> \r\n</p>\r\n<p style=\"text-align:center;\">\r\n\t<img src=\"img/uploads/20160702115150sRJKVrbt4yzh3WQg.jpg\" width=\"600\" height=\"800\" title=\" \" alt=\" \" data-ratio=\"1.33333333\" data-format=\"jpeg\"> \r\n</p>\r\n<div>\r\n</div>\n\n"}